The paper deals with the construction of packings in Grassmannian space, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The use of representation theory suggests a connection to computational geometry (cs.CG) and group theory (cs.GR). Finally, the optimization aspect of the packings suggests a connection to combinatorial optimization (cs.CO).
